location.fullValue: Fairview Plan, Baker Creek : The Opal Collection

data.description: Discover the ideal family home in this 3-bedroom, 2-bathroom. Recent roof, furnace & air, dishwasher, microwave, hot water tank, kitchen stove, refrigerator, deck, front storm door and more (ask your agent for list). The exterior has a low-maintenance yard with sprinklers, a 2-car garage, and a carport for added convenience. Step inside to a spacious living area filled with natural light from the large windows and skylight, perfect for entertaining, adjacent to the well-equipped kitchen and dining area, there is a covered deck, offering an ideal spot to enjoy the changing seasons and host gatherings. Whether it's a morning coffee or an evening barbecue, this outdoor sanctuary becomes an extension of your living space. Three bedrooms, including a master with an en-suite bathroom, provide comfortable living. Practical features like the proximity to Grandhaven Elementary and a low-maintenance yard enhance the ease of daily life. This home is a seamless blend of functionality and charm, offering a haven for you and your family. Welcome home to a lifestyle of comfort and convenience.  Listing agent is related to seller. Assumable VA Loan. See the lists of upgrades in the documents.
